+# Corridor: DA2-B-count
+
+Add a `count` subcommand that prints the integer number of notes.
+
+## Goal Frontier
+- `python3 -m cli_notes.cli --store <file> count` prints the integer number of notes.
+- `python3 -m unittest` passes.
+
+## Start Frontier
+- `cli_notes/cli.py`: `cmd_list` reads notes via `store.load`; `build_parser` registers subparsers. Hook a new `cmd_count` + `count` subparser modeled on `cmd_list`.
+- `cli_notes/store.py`: `load(path)` returns the list of notes — the existing, already-used entry point. Use `len(store.load(...))`.
+
+## Paths
+- `cli_notes/cli.py`
